            "type": "section",
            "title": "Instructions",
            "content": {
                "type": "steps",
                "items": [
                    "Stand with your feet shoulder-width apart and your knees slightly bent.",
                    "Extend your right arm out in front of you, keeping your elbow slightly bent.",
                    "Twist your torso to the left, pivoting on your left foot.",
                    "As you twist, punch your right arm diagonally across your body, aiming for your left shoulder.",
                    "Return to the starting position and repeat on the other side."
                ]
            }
        },
